1
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:05,860
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:09,930
[Episode 4]

3
00:01:16,220 --> 00:01:18,880
[Auspicious Mists of Grace and Peace]

4
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:00,040
Rise.

5
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:02,630
Thank you, Your Majesty.

6
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:09,840
Do you know why I punished you?

7
00:02:10,750 --> 00:02:12,120
Your Majesty,

8
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:14,000
I do not know.

9
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:18,460
You stayed overnight
at General's Mansion yesterday?

10
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:20,680
Yes.

11
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,630
Nonsense!

12
00:02:22,190 --> 00:02:24,079
You and Simo are not yet married.

13
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,470
If this gets out,

14
00:02:25,870 --> 00:02:28,800
the reputation of General and Grand Tutor
will be damaged!

15
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,030
From today onwards,

16
00:02:30,310 --> 00:02:32,190
you are not allowed
to set foot in General's Mansion

17
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:34,030
or even meet him.

18
00:02:34,750 --> 00:02:35,840
Do you understand?

19
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:39,840
I'll obey your instructions, Your Majesty.

20
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:50,870
When did you and His Majesty
know each other?

21
00:02:53,079 --> 00:02:55,000
That day, I came back to the palace
with General

22
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,560
to pay respects to you.

23
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,380
And I was lucky enough to see His Majesty.

24
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,430
Is that so?

25
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,430
I heard

26
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:10,590
His Majesty is quite fond of you.

27
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,360
That's not true.

28
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:15,630
Please don't mock me, Your Majesty.

29
00:03:19,750 --> 00:03:21,480
It'd be best if that's not true.

30
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,800
In life,

31
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,640
the most important thing

32
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:27,310
is to know your place.

33
00:03:28,150 --> 00:03:29,870
Otherwise, chaos follows.

34
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:32,960
I understand.

35
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:35,840
Alright.

36
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:37,710
You may leave.

37
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:40,590
You're a smart person.

38
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:43,360
Remember what I told you today.

39
00:03:44,079 --> 00:03:44,910
Yes.

40
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:07,970
What are you doing?

41
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,400
You saw Her Grace yet you didn't bow.

42
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,330
How many heads do you have to spare?

43
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,310
Greetings, Your Grace.

44
00:04:14,310 --> 00:04:16,240
Your manner was utterly improper!

45
00:04:16,870 --> 00:04:19,070
I am merely a flower gardener.

46
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:21,850
I truly don't understand palace etiquette.

47
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,750
Please forgive me, Your Grace.

48
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:24,270
You...

49
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:25,040
Enough.

50
00:04:25,750 --> 00:04:27,410
His Majesty is still waiting.

51
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:40,310
These flowers...

52
00:04:41,850 --> 00:04:43,409
are indeed beautiful,

53
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:45,310
but they are useless.

54
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:52,430
Your Grace,

55
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,630
if flowers and plants are useless,

56
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:57,240
how would the world be this colorful?

57
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,000
Those seem useless

58
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:00,720
can be of great utility.

59
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,430
She does resemble her,

60
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:10,950
but she's still too young after all,

61
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:15,000
not hiding her thoughts at all.

62
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:21,950
Pass my order:

63
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:25,630
select the nearest auspicious date

64
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:29,120
and advance the wedding
of Simo and Jiang Li.

65
00:05:29,390 --> 00:05:30,270
Yes.

66
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:33,430
Your Grace, you mean...

67
00:05:34,310 --> 00:05:36,159
Since it's a grand wedding,

68
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:40,750
we must ensure His Majesty is informed.

69
00:05:41,070 --> 00:05:42,950
I'll see to it at once.

70
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,580
Greetings, Consort Ling.

71
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:09,830
Wait.

72
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,240
I was wondering where the hairpin

73
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,240
the empress dowager gave me was.

74
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,270
It turns out it's on Miss Jiang's head.

75
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:31,310
Miss Jiang,

76
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:33,190
I know this hairpin is rare,

77
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,240
and you've never seen anything like it.

78
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:37,720
It's only natural that you were tempted.

79
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,040
But you should know

80
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:41,159
that those who steal in the palace

81
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:43,159
will have their both hands cut off.

82
00:06:43,390 --> 00:06:45,750
There's no deep grudge between us,

83
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:47,240
let alone any conflict.

84
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,430
Why are you treating me like this?

85
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:54,000
You're merely Grand Tutor's daughter.

86
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:57,050
You truly don't deserve
to have any conflict with me.

87
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:59,270
But what I hate most about you is

88
00:06:59,390 --> 00:07:01,120
how you seek power and influence

89
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:03,240
yet feign high-mindedness deliberately.

90
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:06,310
It's one thing that General,
innocent and sincere, was seduced by you.

91
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:08,240
But recently I heard

92
00:07:08,430 --> 00:07:10,890
you want
to climb into His Majesty's bed too!

93
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:19,830
It seems you're afraid of me.

94
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:23,800
Fine.

95
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:25,680
Then today, I will

96
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:28,040
ruin this pretty face of yours.

97
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:30,770
Let's see
how you'll flaunt yourself after this!

98
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,050
What are you going to do?

99
00:07:39,870 --> 00:07:40,480
You...

100
00:07:57,510 --> 00:07:59,310
Now it's been returned
to its rightful owner.

101
00:07:59,310 --> 00:08:01,360
Consort Ling, if there's nothing else,

102
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,680
I'll take my leave.

103
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,310
If I don't teach you a lesson today,
I'll...

104
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:05,160
Ling!

105
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:14,900
[Zhao State's 10th Prince, Xie Nianzhao]

106
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:19,360
-Greetings, Prince Nianzhao.
-Greetings, Prince Nianzhao.

107
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,390
Ling,

108
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,950
you've been in the palace
for so many years,

109
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:25,120
yet you're still so hot-tempered.

110
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:29,830
No wonder
Jiuzhao never pays any attention to you.

111
00:08:29,830 --> 00:08:30,480
I...

112
00:08:30,950 --> 00:08:31,870
Tell me,

113
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,360
what's so interesting

114
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,220
that you're making such a racket?

115
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,909
Prince Nianzhao,

116
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:40,789
Consort Ling lost her hairpin,

117
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:43,200
and we were just helping her look for it.

118
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,550
Funny thing is,

119
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:47,960
Consort Ling forgot that the hairpin

120
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:50,630
-was actually on her head.
-You stole my hairpin!

121
00:08:50,630 --> 00:08:52,080
Consort Ling, do you have any evidence?

122
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:52,790
Enough.

123
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:55,520
It's just a misunderstanding.

124
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,080
Ling,

125
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:59,480
just put this matter to rest

126
00:08:59,870 --> 00:09:02,960
for my sake, okay?

127
00:09:09,630 --> 00:09:10,550
Sister,

128
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:12,030
let me escort you out.

129
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:13,390
Thank you.

130
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,750
Sir. How much is this?

131
00:09:31,790 --> 00:09:32,790
Ten coins each.

132
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:33,910
Ten coins?

133
00:09:35,130 --> 00:09:35,720
Here.

134
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:38,600
Young Master, you gave me too much.

135
00:09:38,910 --> 00:09:39,840
Keep the change.

136
00:09:39,870 --> 00:09:40,750
Thank you.

137
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,760
Prince Nianzhao, you...

138
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,630
Just call me Nianzhao.

139
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:49,960
It's not proper
to attract too much attention.

140
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:51,550
Nianzhao?

141
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:54,600
Weren't you just escorting me to the gate?

142
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:56,150
Why bring me here?

143
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,910
Considering what you just experienced,

144
00:09:58,910 --> 00:10:00,270
you must be feeling upset.

145
00:10:00,270 --> 00:10:01,000
Just let me

146
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,910
take you to buy something

147
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:03,910
and get a new hair ornament.

148
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:05,910
It might help lift your spirits.

149
00:10:07,630 --> 00:10:09,080
I think

150
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:11,650
you wanted to sneak out
and have fun yourself.

151
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:14,360
Sister, don't expose me.

152
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:16,030
My mother would...

153
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,670
My mother and my elder brother

154
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:21,000
are very strict.

155
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:23,670
Usually, they just make me study at home.

156
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,440
I'm almost dying of boredom.

157
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,870
Sister, let's go.

158
00:10:31,870 --> 00:10:33,400
Let's get something to eat.

159
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,790
Your noodles are here.

160
00:10:34,790 --> 00:10:35,480
Thank you.

161
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,720
Enjoy, you two.

162
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,270
Didn't we come to eat noodles?

163
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,760
Why did you order so much?

164
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,030
Sister,

165
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:50,670
these are all its signature dishes here.

166
00:10:50,670 --> 00:10:51,240
Here.

167
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,120
Try this.

168
00:10:52,870 --> 00:10:54,070
Thank you. Thank you.

169
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:56,030
And this. It's very delicious.

170
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:00,630
By the way,

171
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:03,600
earlier I saw a jade pendant
at your waist.

172
00:11:04,790 --> 00:11:06,200
Where did you get it?

173
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:09,550
My mother left it to me.

174
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:10,840
What's wrong?

175
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,270
Nothing.

176
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:15,790
It just... looks somewhat familiar.

177
00:11:16,870 --> 00:11:17,910
After we finish the noodles,

178
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:19,970
I'll escort you back to your mansion.

179
00:11:20,030 --> 00:11:21,080
Sister, eat.
